{"tid":550942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想去日本滑雪？","createTime":"2018-02-05T08:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T01:47:59.000Z","uid":14095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"edcfab86ee81ec61159dbe472f6e39928fb087d5","tid":550942,"uid":14095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"各位想去日本滑雪既巴打歡迎搵小第一起滑<br />\n我住係東京 長野/新瀉最好 北海道就不了<br />\n呢個雪季我瘋狂去 可以一起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買票訂住宿交通我都冇咩問題[我日本囯內訂］<br />\n<br />\nTg:japanstudent"},{"pid":"8e9d1b7adfa298a29888b5b99d6e6f88f6c9c69a","tid":550942,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"正呀！<br />\n我3月17~22日會係白馬<br />\n<br />\n事關我聯同台灣朋友攪咗個 spring camp<br />\n會有唔同 教練 同 日本pro rider (例如 星野文香) 主持個d workshops<br />\n夜晚就有 party<br />\n<br />\n已經有超過130人參加<br />\n一半香港一半台灣"}]}